(firstQuint)CSCC_ASC Therapy in Patients With Severe Heart Failure.

 Patients with heart failure will be treated with culture expanded adipose tissue derived mesenchymal stem cells from healthy donors stored in nitrogen until use.

 The cells will be injected directly into the myocardium using the NOGA XP method.

 The patients will be followed for 6 months for safety and efficacy registration.

